{"tid":2036142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【急，要人】驚惡歌法同國安法請入","createTime":"2020-05-26T09:45:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T16:14:48.000Z","uid":25817,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"05edb6a85885211099961b2b8927b13040c27aeb","tid":2036142,"uid":25817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:45:01.000Z","msg":"【惡法不可立，信念不可忘】<br />\n聽日5.27惡歌法<br />\n後日5.28國安法<br />\n我知道各位巴絲打都一定好緊張同好忙 <br />\n<br />\n所以我用舊登三寶月黑高飛想勉勵各位要保持信念同希望<br />\n無論前路幾難行都要一齊堅持<br />\n有時間嘅可以Click入條片支持下我<br />\n但冇時間嘅只係需要睇以下文字<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Hope is a good thing<br />\n也許是人間至善<br />\nMaybe the best of things<br />\n而美好的事永不消逝<br />\nAnd no good thing ever dies</span><br />\n<br />\n但如果大家想打破同溫層，令到連登以外可以有更多人睇到<br />\n我懇求大家幫手推post同CLSS<br />\n因為Youtube演算法好睇重頭24小時CLSS數量<br />\n所以標題用【急，要人】呃咗大家入黎<br />\n<br />\n面對港共惡法，我地都冇野阻止到<br />\n但我更加相信200萬人嘅信念同希望會為我地帶黎希望<br />\n睇實身邊每一位手足，大家加油<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=njIvraVuKv0&amp;t=5s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnjIvraVuKv0%26t%3D5s&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA6VJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=f07c72d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=njIvraVuKv0&amp;t=5s</a>"},{"pid":"07b64dede30207f49650545a5672815ed15808d6","tid":2036142,"uid":25817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:50:36.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"7993dc5255cc170baaceddcac9652e4a2ea2ad44","tid":2036142,"uid":25817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:06:21.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"969db4b309ebcd1200d9f02caba2484766aca7e1","tid":2036142,"uid":244058,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:08:15.000Z","msg":"已經睇左 支持<br />\n幫推！"},{"pid":"e81cbdf14d145afbdefba652c237b54ae7795c9b","tid":2036142,"uid":25817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"969db4b309ebcd1200d9f02caba2484766aca7e1","tid":2036142,"uid":244058,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":